secubox-eye-remote (2.1.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

 * Add bootstrap role: mass_storage LUN for U-Boot loading
 * Add TFTP shadow channel via dnsmasq configuration
 * New API: /api/v1/eye-remote/boot-media/ endpoints
 * Implement 4R double-buffer for active/shadow image management
 * Add atomic swap with crash recovery on gadget enable
 * New systemd service: secubox-eye-gadget.service
 * Deprecate: secubox-otg-gadget.sh (moved to boot_media.py logic)

